<p>You can't cancel an Alpha subscription, but you may <a href="/docs/v2/our-platform/tutorials/alpha-streams-market/licensing-alphas#05-Manage-Existing-Bids">cancel the auto-renewing bid</a> that you have for the Alpha. If you have strong reasons to request a cancellation and refund, <a href="/contact">contact us</a> with those reasons for evaluation.</p>

